question.title: reading google sheet rows marked with certain colors
question.body: I am creating a Java application where I need to read google sheets, create objects from the row values and store them in the database. The problem is that I need to read not the whole sheet (tens of thousands rows) but only rows that are highlighted with certain colors. I did not find in the google docs how to set up this search criteria. If someone has done something similar, I will appreciate some pointers.
